OL,5, Four female presenters have lost a bid 
OL,6, to take legal action against the BBC on
OL,7, grounds of equal pay, a judge ruled.   
OL,9,FHowever, their separate claims         
OL,10,Fincluding sex and age discrimination   
OL,11,Fwill go to a full employment tribunal. 
OL,13,FThe BBC has rejected their complaints  
OL,14,Fand successfully argued the women had  
OL,15,Fno grounds to bring an equal pay claim.
OL,17,FMartine Croxall, Annita McVeigh, Karin 
OL,18,FGiannone and Kasia Madera said they    
OL,19,F"remain committed to seeking equal     
OL,20,Fpay".                                  
